Carole André https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carole_Andr%C3%A9 0 Carole André (born 11 March 1953) is a French film actress. She appeared in 34 films between 1967 and 1991, including two films screened at the Cannes Film Festival. Carole_André ( born 11_March_1953 ) is a_French_film_actress .
